{"tid":2050132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒揭華為製投票機「可防可控」　　韓國4月大選文在寅大勝驚爆作弊","createTime":"2020-06-04T02:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T04:17:02.000Z","uid":41355,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"55f6bb71e92428557e310d9ee2b88ad1c9d1351c","tid":2050132,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3185179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3185179&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3e8a735d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3185179&h=7b8d3edc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3185179</a>"},{"pid":"9ee8c7dcbcd197a841ac3eae015ebc8d67de99ef","tid":2050132,"uid":41355,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"韓國（南韓）在今年 4 月 15 日舉行國會大選，適逢新型冠狀病毒（ COVID-19 ）疫情，總統文在寅被認為防疫有成，在大選上所屬的共同民主黨也取得壓倒性的勝利。然而近日，日本《 Newsweek 》報導指出，韓國選舉採用中國企業華為（ HUAWEI ）製造的投票機，有舞弊之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n《 Newsweek 》稱，東亞研究中心（ East Asia Research Center ）發現，選舉統計結果有作弊嫌疑，懷疑由華為製造的點票機和計算系統，數據被修改。而因為 COVID-19 疫情，有些接受防疫隔離的選民，提早透過郵政投票的統計也遭到懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n《 Newsweek 》預計在下週二（ 9 ）刊登更多資訊，但根據東亞研究中心官網，文章指出，比起安全的光州／大田網路，韓國國家通訊委員會這次選擇的是 LG U+ 5G 負責此次投票統計，而 LG 公司使用的是華為所生產的設備，並用於 WiFi 事先投票、投票統計。選舉作弊的操作可能是：韓國選舉使用的服務器可以連結至中國伺服器，中方透過發送指令操弄韓國選舉，但強調，這目前還是尚未證實的情況。<br />\n<br />\n據韓國媒體報導，目前選舉舞弊尚未在國內成為主要新聞。韓媒《朝鮮經濟》報導，韓國通訊委員會在上週四（ 28 ）召開記者會，承認投票統計設備由華為製造，並用近 3 個小時的時間，解釋投票沒有被操作的可能，而中國製設備也不能當作選舉不公的證據。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E9%81%AD%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90-%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92%E6%9B%9D-%E9%96%8B%E7%A5%A8%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0-080734813.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.stock.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%25A2%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%259B%259D-%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0-080734813.html&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3a6f51a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E9%81%AD%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90-%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92%E6%9B%9D-%E9%96%8B%E7%A5%A8%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0-080734813.html</a>"},{"pid":"9a176bca9afb085d3b7894ccba804643ba896f82","tid":2050132,"uid":261913,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:43:32.000Z","msg":"都係用返真票投好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d508b13e692c436ff4c6c58bee4e011712d040","tid":2050132,"uid":346701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9a176bca9afb085d3b7894ccba804643ba896f82","tid":2050132,"uid":261913,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:43:32.000Z","msg":"都係用返真票投好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:56:40.000Z","msg":"一定，電子點票好易黑箱作業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d051366633c24f95644f2c8c4f4de5aa17ddd4d","tid":2050132,"uid":63154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"投票要肉眼望住有個人填張飛放入箱先算！"},{"pid":"3066d576bfb5c9f9087a8257f9737f1a500b30e0","tid":2050132,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"有乜咁出奇, 美國投票機都被人捉到報假數啦"},{"pid":"d8a8d84ec8ba6816697e0d45c46d33d4